      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, reboil a kettle</p><p>Wash and chop the <strong>red gem lettuce </strong>in half widthways and discard the stem</p><p>Cut the <strong>cherry tomatoes</strong> in half</p><p>Chop the <strong>black olives </strong>roughly</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1530.-step-3-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1530.-step-3-x400.jpg",
