            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1530.-step-3-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>drained potatoes</strong> to a baking tray and crush them gently with a fork</p><p>Sprinkle the <strong>capers</strong> over the<strong> crushed potatoes</strong></p><p>Drizzle everything with <strong>olive oil</strong>, season with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and give everything a gentle mix up</p><p>Put the tray in the oven for 15-20 min, or until golden and crisp</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1530.-step-4-x200.jpg",
