      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the potatoes are cooking, add the <strong>eggs</strong> to a pot of <strong>boiling water</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> over a high heat (salt prevents the eggs from cracking!)</p><p>Boil for an initial 4 min</p><p>After 4 min add the <strong>green beans</strong> and boil for a further 3-4 min or until the beans are tender</p><p>Once done, drain and run everything under <strong>cold water</strong></p>",
